Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the Space Field, the Duel between Kaito and V has started!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing Dyson Sphere, V’s invisible Number, Kaito’s attacks aren't working at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, it finally appears in front of us…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a ridiculously large Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Dyson Sphere is a space fortress\N capable of engulfing the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ability is unmatchable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, all of your attacks will be useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...! You're saying I can't attack it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right. When Dyson Sphere has Overlay Units attached to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is able to negate all of my opponent's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why my attack didn't go through?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I know its effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know exactly what you are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the one who taught you how to Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V was Kaito's teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Tron... No, when my father went missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my family was split apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My younger brothers were taken\N to an orphanage as such a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to investigate the truth behind my father's disappearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed with Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is when I met you brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I watched you brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have very well saw myself and my brothers in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you wished to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to acquire the power to protect your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I taught you about Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I never expected that I would battle you again in this manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you are trying to get in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not show you any mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,502)}"Number 56: The Great Decisive Battle of Outer Space!\N Neo Galaxy-Eyes Strikes Back"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere's Attack Power is 2800.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Galaxy-Eyes' Attack Power is 3000.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you think I won’t declare an attack, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems you still aren't completely aware of Dyson Sphere’s second ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Dyson Sphere's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,522)}By detaching one Overlay Unit, it can attack directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(629,515)}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,528)}A direct attack with 2800 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that attack connects… Kaito will…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Photonize!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is a Light-Attribute Monster on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my opponent’s attack is negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my Light Monster’s Attack Power will increase equal to the Attack Power of my opponent’s attacking Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he utilized the opponent’s direct attack to his own advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s useless. I have already foreseen your Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Space Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there is a Dyson Sphere on the field, it can negate the activation of my opponent’s Trap Card and destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain I suffered from Dr. Faker, and my grudge against him for tearing my family apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe that Kaito… is being beaten this badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man's Dueling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is scarily flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have 200 of your Life remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This match has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you collapse over here, what will happen to Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need your sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right! Shut your mouth, Foolma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! Yuma may be an idiot, but he isn't some foolish pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Note: Tonma is an Asian pun used to call someone an idiot. It comes from the word "ton", which means pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How surprising, Yuma, that you actually treat Kaito as an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito is the son of Dr. Faker, the one who betrayed Kazuma-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, he is a Numbers Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaito survives, then that means…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day you will be hunted by him as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I once had a Duel with Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, no matter how he thinks, he is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my goal too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma-{\i1}san{\i0} did treasure that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that ideal was completely wrecked and betrayed by Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you forgive...that kind of person’s son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized all of the truth, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you... Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat you and recover your Number!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you do not understand our hatred in the least, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dyson Sphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can negate attacks, and is able to attack directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although at first glance that effect seems invincible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it! Dyson Sphere’s weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Overlay Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can send all Overlay Units to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that Monster now changes to “can be destroyed by battle”!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected no less from Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere can only negate battles when it has Overlay Units.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Kaito’s Magic card,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere’s invincible effect is negated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, even the effect of “only Numbers can be destroy Numbers” is negated too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Dyson Sphere has become a huge pile of scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Stream of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already expect that move as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate another effect of Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Dyson Sphere is attacked while it has no Overlay Units,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can recover Overlay Units from Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I activate Dyson Sphere’s first effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it has Overlay Units, my opponent’s attack will be negated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s futile, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is capable off destroying Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito's Life has fallen to 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When next turn comes…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...set one card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A direct attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Equipment Magic, Gravity Blaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, this card can increase equipped Monster’s Attack Power by 400,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plus it can negate my the opponent's Monster’s effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he attack directly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would V do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you should know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mere victory won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true victory will only determined when I crush Galaxy-Eyes , your embodiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Mirror Shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:11:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By halving my Life, this card can negate the damage I received!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible! There is no way he can win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kai…Kaito…is going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito's Life is 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V's Life remains untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for Kaito, under these circumstances…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, it's very painful, isn't it?\N Unbearable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, you can release yourself from all kinds of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the mission as a Numbers Hunter, or the pain brought by Haruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final act of pity I can give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, not even for a single moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did I ever consider Haruto as my pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's… Haruto is my everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has always given me hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not on myself or on Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...! This card is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This card will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...activate the Magic Card, Feelings Towards the Future!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What’s that card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I…I can’t believe you have a card I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A card like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was in your deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how much you may know about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way you can know about this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this card is the only one in my life my father gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito’s father…Dr. Faker gave him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I haven’t used this card even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd... You hate your father so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you put that card in your deck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you ever do something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would want to protect their family, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you guys wish to protect your own family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why Kaito will always hold that card,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he has hope for his own family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope for his family?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Kaito-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t need you to speak for my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic card, Feelings Towards the Future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can Summon three Monsters with different levels from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revive, Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Photon Slasher! Photon Pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Monsters Special Summoned by this effect will have their Attack Power changed to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s meaningless, Kaito! Their Attack Points are zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they're different levels. What good can they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Shift Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can change all levels of Monsters on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all to be the same of the Monster with highest level!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I raise all Monsters’ Level to eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Eight Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon, Photon Slasher, and Photon Pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these three Monsters to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great Galaxy of Reversal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the rolling waves of light and show your mighty form!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Descend, my very soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, I activate the effect of Field Magic, Cosmic Frontier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I Xyz summon successfully, I can draw one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Neo Galaxy Eyes' effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Howling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Neo Galaxy-Eyes is Xyz Summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can negate effects of all Monsters except of itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dyson Sphere is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Big Bang Panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card changes all face-up Magic or Trap Cards on my opponent’s field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to my opponent's Monster’s Overlay Units!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with every additional Overlay Unit, my Monster gains 800 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:17:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by detaching one Overlay Unit, I activate the effect of Neo Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It absorbs all Overlay Units from Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Every Overlay Unit absorbed, it gains 500 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 6800 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Neo Galaxy-Eyes can attack up to the Number of Overlay Units it absorbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that moment, somewhere deep within my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing you all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Photon Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, so is this your strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After revenge, only emptiness remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V, no, Christopher Arklight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a long time since someone used that name to address me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's V’s real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with my father, I have given up my family’s name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I did try to save my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when my father returned from the Parallel Worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his heart was already consumed by vengeance towards Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, I guess that is what “parental relationship” is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fight because I resist my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day when I manage to resolve Haruto’s case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will settle the score with Dr. Faker using my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you have already become this strong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris, I will inherit your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will settle the score with Tron in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are indeed my…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...little brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me! I will definitely make it to the next stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Orbital 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu…But the glider is out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I just got stared down...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will undergo urgent operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for 3 seconds. 1…2…3!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron and Dr. Faker...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When two of them took action,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was transported to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that was your father’s intention, who is in the Astral World currently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father wished for me to stop Tron and Dr. Faker, together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:21:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! I'll do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give those egocentric adults a lesson too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.23,0:22:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the scorching Magma Field, the Duel between Shark and IV has finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shocking truths revealed by IV, plus Tron’s sudden appearance…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this field, his Monsters…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe you would give Numbers to…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can attack eight times in a row?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dueling isn't a tool for rage and revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shark Torpedoed! The Nightmarish Fanservice"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome how you beat Dyson Sphere, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that means Kaito will use Dyson Sphere when we fight him next.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito is truly our greatest enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'im!
